# NBA Game Day

Welcome to the NBA Game Day web application! This project provides an exciting way to keep track of NBA games, featuring team highlights and upcoming matchups.

## Table of Contents

- [Features](#features)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [License](#license)

## Features

- Display of featured NBA teams with their logos and colors.
- Upcoming game schedule presented in a table format.
- Engaging quote to capture the essence of the NBA.

## Installation

To get started, clone the repository and open the `index.html` file in your web browser.

```bash
git clone <repository-url>
cd <repository-folder>
open index.html

<table>
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Matchup</th>
            <th>Date</th>
            <th>Time</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td>Lakers vs. Bulls</td>
            <td>Oct 15, 2024</td>
            <td>7:00 PM</td>
        </tr>
        <!-- Additional rows -->
    </tbody>
</table>
